\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

 the 
\begin_inset Formula $i+1^{st}$
\end_inset

 subspace will accommodate more inconclusive rate than the 
\begin_inset Formula $i^{th}$
\end_inset

 subspace, the 
\begin_inset Formula $Q_{i}^{opt}(Q)$
\end_inset

 curves will intersect (see part (b) of Fig.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "Fig2"

\end_inset

 for an example).
\end_layout

